# CODEOWNERS for GithubAutoDev
# Code owner auto-review requests. PRD §2 module 8 relies on this file.
#
# Format: <path> <@owner or @team>+

# Default: maintainers own everything not matched below
*                           @maintainers

# Pipeline infrastructure — stricter review (security-sensitive)
/.github/workflows/         @maintainers @sec-team
/.github/actions/           @maintainers @sec-team

# Protocol / spec docs — architectural ownership
/docs/                      @architects
/CLAUDE.md                  @architects

# Issue templates (input to triage — untrusted surface)
/.github/ISSUE_TEMPLATE/    @maintainers

# Label taxonomy — protocol primitive, maintainers only
/.github/labels.yml         @maintainers
/docs/labels.md             @maintainers
